name: Healthy Plane
description:
Healthy Plane is an offline sidescroller-shooter game, where you can destroy the unhealthy foods.
Avoid fats and sugars and survive 10 waves on each level!

  • Be focused and fast.
  • Survive and complete the 15 levels.
  • Colourful, whacky design.
  • Dominate the leaderboard.

Get Healthy Plane now and have fun!
